title: Game of the week: Lake Travis (7-0) at Westlake (7-0)
text:
7:30 p.m. Friday, Chaparral Stadium
Quarterback: Lake Travis junior Charlie Brewer has completed 73 percent of his passes this season while throwing for 1,334 yards and 21 touchdowns. In addition to being Westlake’s leading rusher, junior Sam Ehlinger has tossed 25 touchdown passes with no interceptions. Edge: Westlake
